How to build AFoundation

1. mkdir build
2. cd build
3. 
	3.1 Ubuntu environment: you should modify wayland path if your wayland is not installed in /usr/lib
		cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DHW_PLATFORM=UBUNTU_OS ../
	3.2 embedded Linux:  you should set your SDK path if is not installed at /workspace/harman/
		source /workspace/harman/elina/2.0.2015143A/environment-setup-corei7-64-elina-linux
		cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/workspace/harman/elina/2.0.2015143A/sysroots/corei7-64-elina-linux/usr -DHW_PLATFORM=LINUX_OS ../
	3.3 other
	    cmake ../
4. make VERBOSE=1;make install
5. the library is at path build/lib/

